'''''Quicksilver''''' was a [[Corellia/Legends|Corellian]] courier ship used by [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] to deliver gifts to [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Sarn Shild]] from [[Jiliac Desilijic Tiron]]. Solo was paid 10,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] for the job, though it did little to help the Hutts from an attack by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

